original_title: 美少女戦士セーラームーン　外伝 ダーク・キングダム復活篇
overview: Usagi and friends are enjoying summer vacation, until Queen Beryl and the Shitennou are revived. The musical was recorded on August 12, 1993 at the Gotanda U-Port Hall in Tokyo, Japan.
title: Sailor Moon - An Alternate Legend - Dark Kingdom Revival Story
